name: Pocong Kembar Siam
description:
An Indonesian ghost that is said to be the soul of a dead person trapped in their shroud. Conjoined twins Pocong is responding to the Indonesian horror cinema during 2010-ish decade. More weird for the title to get more audience, like a clickbait nowadays.

5 edition
